{"tid":186212,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫學jj]副廠藥會唔會令人過敏？","createTime":"2017-04-04T05:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T05:58:24.000Z","uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0f674623349b535332ef0d1d3264f361e628af","tid":186212,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我食一隻原廠藥抗生素唔會過敏既。<br />\n但今日食左隻副廠藥好似有啲過敏反應<br />\n<br />\n因為需要成分一樣，但制作過程有機會唔同<br />\n想問下同一隻藥唔同廠會唔會令到人過敏?"},{"pid":"921c630990c65c7b74596e8323e7a3161764fc7b","tid":186212,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"正常就唔會嘅 但係你話製作運輸個啲過程就好難講"},{"pid":"62fb7ec84a5a42a9512fc41a7099f5dc551b4b56","tid":186212,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"你問呢樣問題就例如你話食日本富士蘋果同美國蘋果有咩分別一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  產地，種法，氣候唔同，梗係會唔一樣<br />\n<br />\n正廠多數睇quality, 副廠冇r&amp;d, 除左sandoz 果d 大間既副廠，好多細廠都係拎左條過左專利既方就用價錢打入個market"},{"pid":"8926568e18e9adc1e776a1d3feccd492b534826c","tid":186212,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常就唔會嘅 但係你話製作運輸個啲過程就好難講</blockquote><br />\n係囉,呢隻藥都食過好多次都冇問題<br />\n今日唔知做咩食完呢隻副廠藥就有反應<br />\n所以想睇下有冇巴打知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d118332c9d6d0b0c20f9ec39a1ed6edc4d8b50","tid":186212,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你問呢樣問題就例如你話食日本富士蘋果同美國蘋果有咩分別一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  產地，種法，氣候唔同，梗係會唔一樣<br />\n<br />\n正廠多數睇quality, 副廠冇r&amp;d, 除左sandoz 果d 大間既副廠，好多細廠都係拎左條過左專利既方就用價錢打入個market</blockquote><br />\n明白巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該你<br />\n咁睇黎要叫醫生開返隻正廠藥先得<br />\n希望唔好因為咁搞到我連隻正廠藥都過敏埋<br />\n如果唔係就死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3605ad4e1d58ed4c106689188b0cfdbc34d62297","tid":186212,"uid":79967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"Active ingredient成份雖然一樣<br />\n但inactive ingredient可能唔同<br />\n可能你對某啲/隻inactive ingredient有過敏"},{"pid":"c23cdd170696137d327aa03cc6ae9e2ad908f436","tid":186212,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Active ingredient成份雖然一樣<br />\n但inactive ingredient可能唔同<br />\n可能你對某啲/隻inactive ingredient有過敏</blockquote><br />\nTHX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}